data.description: Come call Hidden Valley Estates home today! Situated on over half an acre, this home offers tons of privacy. On the first floor you will find a large family room with wood floors, wood beams, a wood burning fireplace and tons of builtins. The kitchen has ample counter space, cabinets and overlooks the eat in nook. The formal dining room is a great space for entertaining, or could be used as a bar room or sitting room. There's a spacious back porch with skylights and ez breeze windows for you to enjoy all seasons outside. Upstairs is an office and three additional bedrooms all with hardwood floors. Also on the second floor is the primary suite, complete with wood burning fireplace, attached en suite and walk in closet. The basement is perfect for making an additional bedroom/living space complete with a full bathroom and tons of storage. With close proximity to 95 and 288 this home offers something for everyone in the family.
